Ladies And Gentlemen;
´As we reached 5000€ we want to give a special free gift to every one who pledged A, B or C... So Stay connected, we Will Snow you ´as soon as possible the gift...
What I could say about this gift is that it's a special mini... Hammer, wrench... 😊

In the last few weeks we have pretty much caught up on almost everything from all of the previous Kickstarters, as things stand there are;  
3 x 32mm Cars Pledges to go out, the last few cars moulds are being redone as we speak as they weren't quite able last out; once complete the last few pledges will be delivered. Should be in next week or so.  
4 x 15mm Cars Pledges to be delivered; the Working Cars Moulds gave out with only 4 sets to go! Again, we have a Caster working on the new master moulds right now to deliver the last 4 sets and the last 4 pledges will be out asap!

