- I've been sending out European parcels all week, and those are almost complete. The last of them will go out early this week. I've also been dropping in a couple of US / ROW parcels with each batch so the first of those should start arriving fairly soon as well.Its my aim to have everything done well before the end of May and i'm on track to complete that.
